---
import Legal from '../../layouts/Legal.astro';
import { withBase } from '../../i18n/content';
const privacyHref = withBase('/en/privacy');
---
<Legal lang="en" path="/referral-terms" title="Referral Program Terms" updated="July 1, 2026">
  <p>The <strong>PardeSantos</strong> Referral Program lets partners (brokers, real estate agents, notaries, municipal agents and similar) earn a commission for referring prospects who close a purchase. By registering, the partner accepts these terms.</p>

  <h2>1. Commission</h2>
  <p>The partner will receive a commission of <strong>7% (seven percent) of the sale value</strong> of the product actually <strong>closed and settled</strong> by a prospect referred and registered by that partner.</p>

  <h2>2. Referral registration</h2>
  <p>For a referral to be valid, the prospect must be registered by the partner through the site form or the agreed channel, <strong>before</strong> that prospect has initiated contact on their own. If the same prospect is referred by more than one partner, the first to register them will be recognized.</p>

  <h2>3. Payment conditions</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>The commission is earned only when the sale has been <strong>paid in full</strong> (not on reservations, deposits or cancelled sales).</li>
    <li>Commission payment will be made within a reasonable period after full settlement of the sale, by the means the parties agree (including, if agreed, payment in crypto).</li>
    <li>If a sale is cancelled, refunded or not closed, no commission is earned.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Nature of the relationship</h2>
  <p>The program <strong>does not create an employment, subordination, partnership or agency relationship</strong> between the partner and PardeSantos. The partner acts on their own behalf as an independent referrer and is responsible for any tax obligations arising from the commissions received.</p>

  <h2>5. Partner conduct</h2>
  <p>The partner agrees to present product information truthfully, without making performance, durability or warranty promises that are not backed in writing by PardeSantos.</p>

  <h2>6. Changes and term</h2>
  <p>PardeSantos may modify or terminate the program at any time, honoring commissions already earned on sales closed before the change.</p>

  <h2>7. Data processing</h2>
  <p>Partner and referred-prospect data are processed under our <a href={privacyHref}>Privacy Notice</a>.</p>

  <h2>8. Contact</h2>
  <p>To enroll or ask questions: <a href="mailto:oscaromargp@gmail.com">oscaromargp@gmail.com</a> · 6121077805.</p>
</Legal>
